---
import { ArrowRight } from 'lucide-react';
---

<section class="bg-gradient-to-br from-brand-primary to-brand-primary-light py-20 px-4 relative overflow-hidden">
  <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 -translate-y-1/2 translate-x-1/3 w-96 h-96 bg-white/10 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
  <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 translate-y-1/3 -translate-x-1/4 w-72 h-72 bg-brand-dark/10 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
  
  <div class="container-brand relative z-10 text-center">
    <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-display font-bold text-white mb-6">
      Mulai perjalanan fitness-mu hari ini
    </h2>
    <p class="text-white/80 text-lg md:text-xl mb-10 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
      Bergabunglah dengan ratusan wanita Banjarmasin lainnya yang telah mencapai tubuh ideal dan hidup lebih sehat bersama kami.
    </p>
    <a href="/daftar" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center bg-white text-brand-primary px-8 py-4 rounded-full font-bold text-lg hover:bg-brand-light transition-all shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-1 group">
      Daftar Trial Gratis Sekarang
      <ArrowRight class="ml-2 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform" />
    </a>
  </div>
</section>
